title: Chix cross country finishes 2nd, 4th in OK Black
text: Chix cross country finishes 2nd, 4th in OK Black Comment Posted Oct. 21, 2015 at 10:18 PM Updated at 10:18 PM Posted Oct. 21, 2015 at 10:18 PM Holland, Mich. The Zeeland East girls placed fourth in the OK Black Conference race. Pacing the Chix was Carissa Macomber (fifth) in 16:31. The Chix finished tied for second in the overall standings. The boys finished fourth overall but placed third at the conference meet behind John Groendyke (third) in 16:36, Kody DeHaan (ninth) in 17:03, Schaeffer Ailes (10th) in 17:03. By Staff report
